{"tid":1599174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候做好文宣，同所有淺黃/淺藍講雙普選既重要性","createTime":"2019-09-27T23:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T00:20:09.000Z","uid":54303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2931390fcaa0a2bf25615660fd2670ab0a572e1e","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7FWKeZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7FWKeZ.jpg&h=e01b43ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQ9gKe0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQ9gKe0.png&h=3f56b9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果立法會同特首唔係由香港人控制，試問我地點樣可以「徹查」同埋「嚴懲」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由一個親共政府去成立「獨立調查委員會」，政府會唔會暗中施壓要求佢地唔好查中聯辦、解放軍等等既角色？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且，無普選只會有下一個林鄭，會有另一條「逃犯條例」之類既低能野。有普選先可以有個貼地、尊重市民既政府，從根本上解決種種社會矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請各位努力宣揚。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f7bf68ab82871bcfea04cc61457a94aebd2fd7","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a837530e9d026087a4f57b5ac8efb41bc83c637c","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:25:06.000Z","msg":"睇番林鄭果個「對話會」，有感而發。<br />\n警察只係安全套，清唔清算佢地都唔會傷害共產黨。但係雙普選、港人治港，咁就可以有個城牆守住香港。"},{"pid":"12ab534aeb279beb19961d56a2cfa1bfbfa25b6f","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:26:19.000Z","msg":"終極目標係拖到支爆，共產黨倒台、中國大亂。咁我地就可以係美軍庇護之下安全、自由生活。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4677878718d31cb1d0a10ff563393c75a0ecee54","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:27:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"515e215a892592ce641362b174cfb9e70657d355","tid":1599174,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"心態要調整<br />\n求幫推 或多或少有幫助<br />\n［反省］我發現好多人都搵唔到方向及定位 入嚟啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"59dfd370fc8bcd4f93dd8fb813f8ac7747ad15e3","tid":1599174,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8257a4a7606831285b6f39211aa3915c200eaff","tid":1599174,"uid":264865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"呢個要推。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69b1fa29854359eabb0962894d461ac95faa380","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54021c16b9d41aaac79320f06af38901182e64a0","tid":1599174,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:41:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75ab45b40b0f5cd82f3fcc9575bcec558671316a","tid":1599174,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31bf82b3978dd727e5f3175a485566382ebc156","tid":1599174,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:42:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ad95538d1e52eb395fde69f7a2c8158e8382a91","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8257a4a7606831285b6f39211aa3915c200eaff","tid":1599174,"uid":264865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:31:40.000Z","msg":"呢個要推。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:42:34.000Z","msg":"岩岩先見到個post問港獨點樣成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直布羅陀點樣我地咪點樣囉，小國當然要成為大國既保護領，而且要為大國提供利用價值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以港獨唔係要對本土宣傳就夠，要搞港獨就要去美國大力遊說"},{"pid":"d2ce4cb168dc4298d097b5577d07dcf2f59dc3be","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d325e2e380cc1a0293fe5d44f21d4075dbd066f","tid":1599174,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33ca964bbbf5481c66b038dc7d976de0f340b45","tid":1599174,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:20:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}